4Geeks Academy offers a course in AI Machine Learning Engineering. This course is designed for beginners and provides the skills needed to start a career as a data scientist. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker (Google Data Studio), and Streamlit, as well as statistics and industry-standard tools. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course also includes real-life case studies and allows students to develop their own AI projects. The duration of the course is 16 weeks, with 3 classes held weekly. The class size is limited to 12 people maximum. No previous experience is required, and the course is available in both English and Spanish. Upon completion, students will receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop